age speaking opportunities at conferences and other in-person events Oversee the execution of the Smart Contract Summit developer and community conference Collaborate with the executive team to develop their point of view and provide media training/coaching as needed to help establish them as experts in the field Develop a crisis communications practice and playbook Build and lead a team of exceptional communications professionals; manage a team of writers, videographers, press agencies, social media managers, event organizers and content producers Bachelor's degree or above 7+ years of experience in communications, marketing or related fields Exceptional written, oral, interpersonal, and storytelling skills to express messages concisely and compellingly A demonstrated ability to understand a complex technical subject matter and to simplify and explain it to a broader audience Demonstrate grace under fire and ability to work in a fast-paced working environment, ability to deliver a quality product under time-bound and stressful circumstances A proven track record of building long-term, beneficial relationships with media and analysts Experience successfully managing agencies, clients and/or direct reports Experience working with global companies with and audience bases in multiple languages Experience working on developer tools, technical products, and open-source a plus Ability to keep up to date with the latest news and discoveries in the blockchain and technology space Passion for the blockchain space and its power to change the world for the better This role is location agnostic anywhere in the world, though we ask that you overlap some working hours with Eastern Standard Time (EST). About Us Smart contracts are on track to revolutionize how all agreements work, through an entirely new system of technologically enforced contract guarantees. Chainlink enables next-generation smart contracts that can be written about any/all events in the real world; the details of our approach can be found in Chainlink's whitepaper. Chainlink is well recognized for providing highly secure and reliable blockchain connectivity to the world's largest enterprises, such as Google, Oracle, SWIFT, and many more. This is a unique opportunity to join one of the top companies developing cutting-edge blockchain technology while working closely together with a team of experienced senior developers. Chainlink is an Equal Opportunity Employer.* ", 
